-- XCMG May Buy Schwing Stake Within Two Weeks, Handelsblatt Says
-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 2012-03-26T06:06:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-26/xcmg-may-buy-schwing-stake-within-two-weeks-handelsblatt-says.html
China ’s  XCMG Construction Machinery
Co. (000425)  may conclude an agreement to acquire a stake in Schwing GmbH
within two weeks,  Handelsblatt reported , citing unidentified
people in the industry.  The size of the stake that XCMG plans to acquire is still
“unclear,” Handelsblatt said.  -- Editor: Chris Peterson  To contact the reporter on this story:
